  "2171640": {
    "name": "Code Reactors: 符文谐鸣士",
    "steam_appid": 2171640,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《CodeReactors》是一款融合了“卡组构建”与“2D动作”的肉鸽（Roguelike）RPG。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发动魔法无需复杂的指令。根据战况用“咒文卡（Spell Card）”组建牌组，只需一个按键即可释放。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是，释放的时机由你决定。看穿敌人的破绽，将构建好的连击（Combo）叩击在敌人身上吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/8524c52b4cd69b9c3dba7a5b7d79bec6.poster.avif?t=1766927302\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/8524c52b4cd69b9c3dba7a5b7d79bec6.webm?t=1766927302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/8524c52b4cd69b9c3dba7a5b7d79bec6.mp4?t=1766927302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1. 以最强连击为目标的卡组构建！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得的咒文卡，要按什么顺序发动？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个组合正是你最强的武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・火牌组： 燃烧对手给予持续伤害，同时通过高火力连击猛攻！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・雷牌组： 提高暴击率，发出会心的一击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・冰牌组： 冻结敌人停止其行动，用强力的一击粉碎敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/e0bfc2f7ec69d6d767db440b7c7e3547.poster.avif?t=1766927302\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/e0bfc2f7ec69d6d767db440b7c7e3547.webm?t=1766927302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/e0bfc2f7ec69d6d767db440b7c7e3547.mp4?t=1766927302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2. 肉鸽特有的“一期一会”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次进入迷宫（地牢），地形、获得的卡牌、敌人的配置都会发生变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，还有能剧烈改变你策略的“遗物（Relic）”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找出与强力遗物的协同效应（Synergy），开发出足以破坏游戏平衡的“超模连击”吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/6551a323d10a9f9e5749b835f0feb088.avif?t=1766927302\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras_big/6551a323d10a9f9e5749b835f0feb088.webp?t=1766927302 width=1560 height=318 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3. 时尚的攻防</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻击交给牌组，但防御和回避取决于你的操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看穿敌人的攻击模式，通过完美闪避和格挡（Parry）创造机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请享受卡牌游戏的策略性和动作游戏的紧张感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/7e1fbc9878730ca6c78389299254e3d2.poster.avif?t=1766927302\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/7e1fbc9878730ca6c78389299254e3d2.webm?t=1766927302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/7e1fbc9878730ca6c78389299254e3d2.mp4?t=1766927302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔法使少女“向阳（Himari）”误入了一个由5位魔女创造的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与恶魔少女“伊芙（Eve）”一起，为了解开围绕世界的“最初的魔法”之谜，以最深处为目标挑战迷宫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来吧，组建最强的牌组，攻略魔女们的世界吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直播指南</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论个人还是法人，都欢迎进行实况直播或投稿视频！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以开启收益化。各位玩家的介绍将成为开发团队的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/1036a98b33a4dc3a4bc8d9c441483b8b.poster.avif?t=1766927302\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/1036a98b33a4dc3a4bc8d9c441483b8b.webm?t=1766927302\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2171640/extras/1036a98b33a4dc3a4bc8d9c441483b8b.mp4?t=1766927302\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
